'''Félicien Kabuga''' ( 1 Werurwe mu 1933   -) ni rwiyemezamirimo yavutse mu Rwanda akaba aregwa na kimwe mu itsembabwoko bibi mu mateka, mu jenoside abantu barenga 800.000 mu Rwanda mu 1994.<ref>https://web.archive.org/web/20191027015941/https://trialinternational.org/latest-post/felicien-kabuga/</ref>

Félicien Kabuga yamye ahakana ko atagize uruhara muri jenoside kandi akomeza gutangaza ko ari umwere. 

Yafatiwe i Paris ku ya 16 Gicurasi 2020 afite imyaka 84. Ikigaragara ni uko yabaga mu nkengero z'umurwa mukuru w'Ubufaransa mu ndangamuntu. 
